{"type":"question","id":10688,"title":"乘坐Hi-Level客车是一种什么样的体验？","uid":4516,"topics":[14],"contents":"这是美国的一种<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hi-Level\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">双层客运列车</a>，名字叫Hi-Level。<s>比其他客车车厢高不知道哪里去了</s>（其实<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hi-Level#/media/File:AMTK_F40PH_292_and_a_SDP40F_with_Train_4,_The_Southwest_Limited_near_Darling,_AZ_in_March_1981_(28728387250).jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">并没有</a>）。起源于上世纪50年代。<br>\n外面长这样的：<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG/440px-Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG/440px-Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG/440px-Sante_Fe_Railroad_El_Capitan.JPG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n可以上二楼的餐车跟人谈笑风生，天气好的时候这个景观scenic：<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Pacific_parlour_car.jpg/600px-Pacific_parlour_car.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Pacific_parlour_car.jpg/600px-Pacific_parlour_car.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Pacific_parlour_car.jpg/600px-Pacific_parlour_car.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-10","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}